{"tid":1000290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老】用遮狂篤毛孩　狗主話佢仲想篤眼","createTime":"2019-01-29T10:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T11:16:44.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75398a30dd0c3ab90391e91b1fde9c5a98bc8a46","tid":1000290,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"雨傘當武器？粉嶺阿婆疑篤毛孩眼　狗主拍片喝止<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/bkn-20190129165539528-0129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190129%2Fbkn-20190129165539528-0129_00822_001.html&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=a07b71eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/bkn-20190129165539528-0129_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190129/photo/bkn-20190129165539528-0129_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190129174022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190129%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190129165539528-0129_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190129174022&h=2e40f2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗狗個樣好無辜。<br />\n<br />\n狗是人類的好朋友。惟近日粉嶺有婆婆路經一間舖頭時，竟疑似想用雨傘插狗狗眼睛，幸狗主及時拍片喝止！<br />\n<br />\n影片於周二（29日）上載至Facebook群組「North District 北區」，只見粉嶺聯和墟有狗狗躺在一家舖頭前方，有滿頭白髮的婆婆經過時，用雨傘戳了幾下牠身下的座位。<br />\n<br />\n狗主頓時拍片嚷道︰「篤佢呀，插佢對眼呀！我錄影緊呀，大力啲插落去。今朝又話插佢眼嘅，依家唔插喇？」婆婆回頭看了幾眼後，便慢慢離去。<br />\n<br />\n網友均不值婆婆所為︰「狗仔都冇去搞佢，做咩搞人」、「賓仔喺聯和墟出晒名好乖」、「咁都要蝦隻狗」，又提醒狗主要小心照顧愛犬。<br />\n<br />\n事後，該狗主向各網友致謝：「其實我最初真係好嬲，過咗幾個鐘下咗火氣，又可憐個婆婆，如果佢家人得閒照顧佢就唔會發生呢啲事。好多謝大家，好對不起賓仔，我照顧賓仔唔好」。"},{"pid":"abb9a2995d101ab54f9ad16d00a7ea9540790a83","tid":1000290,"uid":82532,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"咩毛孩&hellip;"},{"pid":"52081351dcaddb2c23f1581d82281031670f1a86","tid":1000290,"uid":66933,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:23:30.000Z","msg":"毛你老母"},{"pid":"fd57ddeb3304bc2c28babcc7ba528674b5828257","tid":1000290,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"今晚食狗肉屌阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7809c996e57d1d6f02e47fba714268dc9b04b53","tid":1000290,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"廢老鬥動物撚"},{"pid":"108410ce0078455ac669821dcf78340e8edee0ab","tid":1000290,"uid":43983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d7809c996e57d1d6f02e47fba714268dc9b04b53","tid":1000290,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"廢老鬥動物撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"你老母生左你隻狗出黎<br />\n供書教學<br />\n唔通又叫動物撚咩？"},{"pid":"7ace57162f8f34bed8a27e80eae64f2d1905a429","tid":1000290,"uid":2545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abb9a2995d101ab54f9ad16d00a7ea9540790a83","tid":1000290,"uid":82532,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"咩毛孩&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"呢個乜撚野term黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bec9166a54a7724f5fef6ff7ff30ca47b8d3ebd","tid":1000290,"uid":194887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"另類自殺方法？想俾狗咬定俾人打"},{"pid":"5ec03a9bae84359fd2cb310ce4724924274ab8b8","tid":1000290,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"108410ce0078455ac669821dcf78340e8edee0ab","tid":1000290,"uid":43983,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d7809c996e57d1d6f02e47fba714268dc9b04b53","tid":1000290,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"廢老鬥動物撚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"你老母生左你隻狗出黎<br />\n供書教學<br />\n唔通又叫動物撚咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"因住俾的告虐狗呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}